title: Superman 23.3 (2013) (Tablet Edition)
description:
I adjusted the resolution and compression of the original scan for easier reading on tablets and to save space. All credit goes to the original scanner for their hard work. I have added 'Tablet Edition' to the name to avoid confusion.

Enjoy and please seed back.



Superman 23.3

By:   	Scott Lobdell, Dan Jurgens, Gene Ha	
Type:   	Comics
Genres:   	Superhero
Series:   	Superman
Publisher:   	DC Comics	
Pub. Date:  	September 18, 2013
Format:         CBZ	

After his last battle with Superman, H'el wakes up on Krypton years before it is destroyed! Can H'el manipulate the Science Counsel, soldiers and countless others including Jor-El, to save the planet? And what does it mean for the birth of Superman if he succeeds?
